  <brief_title>Heated Breathing Circuit on Postoperative Sore Throat After Double-lumen Endobronchial Tube Insertion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Heated Breathing Circuit on Postoperative Sore Throat in Patients Undergoing Double-lumen Endobronchial Tube Insertion</official_title>
